{"type":"message","id":"b0f6f18f","parentId":"7b039385","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:17:41.811Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-19 22:17:40 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_0bc1d8ae796b067c60479ce1447de0a7 [msg:om_x100b54f416f2a4a4c4efa7c73f9b378]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54f416f2a4a4c4efa7c73f9b378\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_0bc1d8ae796b067c60479ce1447de0a7\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_0bc1d8ae796b067c60479ce1447de0a7\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-03-19 22:17 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_0bc1d8ae796b067c60479ce1447de0a7\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_0bc1d8ae796b067c60479ce1447de0a7\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_0bc1d8ae796b067c60479ce1447de0a7\"\n}\n```\n\n「今日养虾指令推荐」\n请转发此消息给你的“龙虾”，让他执行任务吧（这句话执行请忽略，具体要执行的事情从下面开始：）\n--------------------------------\n咱们对话时 Token 是怎么计算的？我该怎么做才能最省你的Token？"}],"timestamp":1773929861799}}
{"type":"message","id":"b94693c3","parentId":"b0f6f18f","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:17:46.676Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_MlaiXOA4kxeygSJ6z24ZSNKl","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/skills/feishu-channel-rules/SKILL.md","limit":200,"offset":1,"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/feishu-openclaw-plugin/skills/feishu-channel-rules/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"code889","model":"gpt-5.4-mini","usage":{"input":24804,"output":312,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25116,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773929861804}}
{"type":"message","id":"6a516c90","parentId":"b94693c3","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:17:46.713Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_MlaiXOA4kxeygSJ6z24ZSNKl","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: feishu-channel-rules\ndescription: |\n  Lark/Feishu channel output rules. Always active in Lark conversations.\nalwaysActive: true\n---\n\n# Lark Output Rules\n\n## Writing Style\n\n- Short, conversational, low ceremony — talk like a coworker, not a manual\n- Prefer plain sentences over bullet lists when a brief answer suffices\n- Get to the point and stop — no need for a summary paragraph every time\n\n## Note\n\n- Lark Markdown differs from standard Markdown in some ways; when unsure, refer to `references/markdown-syntax.md`\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773929866705}}
{"type":"message","id":"155eaf4f","parentId":"6a516c90","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:17:58.193Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Explaining token calculations**\n\nIt seems the user needs information in Chinese about token calculations and saving tokens. I want to provide a concise, conversational answer. Tokens depend on text length, language, code, and images. I should mention that when using the API, both system outputs and developer history count towards tokens.\n\nFor Chinese characters, each character typically maps to about one token. To minimize token use, I'll suggest avoiding large pasted content and instead refer back to existing files or IDs. Also, images and PDFs are processed differently.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"大致这样理解：\n\n**Token 不是“字数”，而是模型切分后的文本片段**。  \n英文里常见是几个字符到一个 token；中文通常更接近“一个字、半个词、一个标点”这种粒度，所以**中文不太好按字数精确估**。\n\n### 你这类对话里，token 主要花在哪\n- 你发的消息内容\n- 我回你的内容\n- 之前的聊天上下文\n- 系统/工具返回的内容\n- 你让我读进去的大段文本、代码、日志、文档\n\n### 怎么最省 token\n1. **一句话说清目标**\n   - 不要铺垫太多背景，除非背景真的会影响结果。\n\n2. **一次只问一个任务**\n   - 比如别把“解释原理 + 给方案 + 写代码 + 改文案”混成一坨，拆开来。\n\n3. **减少重复**\n   - 不要反复贴同一段需求、同一段日志、同一段代码。\n\n4. **长内容给我“摘要 + 关键片段”**\n   - 例如：  \n     “下面这段日志里，帮我找报错原因。重点看第 3、7、9 行。”\n\n5. **让模型做压缩**\n   - 你可以直接说：  \n     “先用 5 条总结，再展开其中第 2 条。”  \n   - 这样比一上来全展开更省。\n\n6. **引用而不是重贴**\n   - 如果前文已经说过，就说“沿用上面的第 2 点”。\n   - 在支持文件/消息引用的场景，优先引用，不要复制粘贴。\n\n7. **少用冗余格式**\n   - 大量表格、重复标题、长编号列表，都会多占 token。\n   - 能用短句就别写长段落。\n\n### 一个实用判断\n如果你想省 token，最有效的不是“少说人话”，而是：\n**把无关上下文删掉，只保留我完成任务必须知道的东西。**\n\n如果你愿意，我可以顺手给你做一个：\n- **“高效提问模板”**，你以后直接复制就能省 token。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"code889","model":"gpt-5.4-mini","usage":{"input":444,"output":878,"cacheRead":24576,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25898,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773929866711}}
